  "text": "HomeShoppingLevel up your holiday gifting game with DESIGNME's latest must-have hair-care bundles, now exclusively at Nordstrom.Photo: Courtesy of DESIGNMELevel up your holiday gifting game with DESIGNME's latest must-have hair-care bundles, now exclusively at Nordstrom.The holiday season calls for stunning hair, and DESIGNME's hair-care bundles are the perfect gift to elevate anyone's festive beauty routine. From the hairstylist's chair to your at-home beauty routine, DESIGNME delivers high-performance, cruelty-free and vegan products loved by customers, stylists and beauty editors alike. Whether you're reaching for volumizing must-haves or shine-boosting favorites, treat yourself (no judgment!) or your bestie to a dreamy routine this holiday season. PUFF.ME Volume Bliss Bundle, $39, available hereGive the gift of healthy, vibrant hair — inside and out. For the Volume Seeker: PUFF.ME Volume Bliss Bundle, $39 (with a value of $54). Give the gift of lush, full-bodied hair with the PUFF.ME Bliss Bundle. A set of four hair-care essentials in a travel-friendly bag that will plump up the volume with a powerhouse routine for body and fullness. The set includes the PUFF.ME Volumizing Shampoo (50ml) and Conditioner (50ml), a duo that cleanses and conditions while enhancing natural volume without weighing down hair. To build durability, the PUFF.ME Treatment Whip (90ml) is an in-shower treatment that strengthens and thickens the hair. To finish, the FAB.ME Leave-In Treatment (50ml) detangles and protects hair from heat damage and breakage, all while boosting shine. These travel-friendly sets arrive in a sleek reusable pouch, perfect for on-the-go styling. PUFF.ME Volume Bliss Bundle, $39, available hereScroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesGLOSS.ME Hydration Bliss Bundle, $39, available hereLackluster strands will love the GLOSS.ME Hydration Bliss Bundle, $39 (with a value of $54), for its ultimate shine and hydration power. Perfect for achieving glossy, hydrated hair, pamper someone special with the GLOSS.ME Bliss Bundle.  This collection targets dry, frizz-prone hair with nourishing formulas that leave locks soft, shiny and manageable — a must-have for winter months. The set includes DESIGNME's crowd-favorites such as the GLOSS.ME Hydrating Shampoo (50ml) and Conditioner (50ml) for a moisturized boost of shine. The GLOSS.ME Hydrating Treatment Mask (90ml) restores hydration and smooths stray ends while the GLOSS.ME Hair Serum (25ml) tames frizz and seals in moisture, for a smooth, sleek finish. All packaged in a sustainable cosmetics pouch that's perfect for travel. GLOSS.ME Hydration Bliss Bundle, $39, available hereDon't miss the opportunity to give the gift of great hair this holiday season. Shop DESIGNME’s top-rated gift sets at Nordstrom and make this holiday one to remember — no wrapping skills required!Please note: Occasionally, we use affiliate links on our site. Learn more about our sponsored affiliate offerings.Subscribe to Our Newsletter",
